{{confused|亞硝酸鹽}}
'''亚硝酸钠'''（[[钠|Na]][[氮|N]][[氧|O]]<sub>2</sub>）常用于鱼类、肉类等食品的[[染色|染色]]和[[防腐|防腐]]。纯净的亚硝酸钠是一种白色至浅黄色[[晶体|晶体]]。它有非常好的水溶性和[[吸湿性|吸湿性]]，水溶液呈弱碱性，[[pH|pH]]约为9，易溶于[[液氨|液氨]]，微溶于[[乙醇|乙醇]]、[[甲醇|甲醇]]、[[乙醚|乙醚]]等[[有机溶剂|有机溶剂]]。亚硝酸钠有咸味，被用来制造假的[[食盐|食盐]]。在空气中，亚硝酸钠会被缓慢氧化成[[硝酸钠|硝酸钠]]（[[钠|Na]][[氮|N]][[氧|O]]<sub>3</sub>），后者是一种强氧化剂。亚硝酸钠遇有机物易发生爆炸。

亚硝酸钠也被用于以下领域：生产[[重氮化合物|重氮化合物]]染料、[[亚硝基化合物|亚硝基化合物]]和其它[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]；[[纤维|纤维]][[纺织品|纺织品]]的染色和[[漂白|漂白]]；[[照相|照相]]；作实验室中的抗[[腐蚀|腐蚀]]剂；作金属涂层中的添加剂；生产[[橡胶|橡胶]]。它的10%水溶液也被用于[[电镀|电镀]]。亚硝酸钠同样被用于人或动物的[[血管|血管]]扩张、支[[气管|气管]]扩张药物中，甚至可以用于[[氰化物|氰化物]]的解毒。

== 制备 ==
亚硝酸钠由[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]与[[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]]、[[二氧化氮|二氧化氮]]混合反应制得：

<math>\rm 2NaOH + NO_2 + NO {=\!=\!=} 2NaNO_2 + H_2O </math>

值得注意的是，该反应需要在无氧条件下进行，否则制得的亚硝酸钠很容易被氧化成[[硝酸钠|硝酸钠]]。

== 用途 ==
=== 日常饮食 ===
亚硝酸盐是普通人日常饮食所需的一部分，存在于很多蔬菜中。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/j.jfca.2008.10.025 | title = Effects of some processing methods on nitrate and nitrite changes in cruciferous vegetables | year = 2009 | last1 = Leszczyńska | first1 = Teresa | last2 = Filipiak-Florkiewicz | first2 = Agnieszka | last3 = Cieślik | first3 = Ewa | last4 = Sikora | first4 = ElżBieta | last5 = Pisulewski | first5 = Paweł M. | journal = Journal of Food Composition and Analysis | volume = 22 | pages = 315 | issue = 4}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wholesomebabyfood.com/nitratearticle.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100416084406/http://www.wholesomebabyfood.com/nitratearticle.htm |archive-date=2010-04-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="sciencedirect.com">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/B0-12-227055-X/00830-0 | title = Nitrates and Nitrites | year = 2003 | last1 = Dennis | first1 = M J | last2 = Wilson | first2 = L A | pages = 4136}}</ref>在34种蔬菜，包括不同种类的白菜、生菜、菠菜、香菜和萝卜等样品中，亚硝酸盐含量通常在1.1到57 mg/kg之间<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/j.foodchem.2009.11.030 | title = Contribution of different vegetable types to exogenous nitrate and nitrite exposure | year = 2010 | last1 = Correia | first1 = Manuela | last2 = Barroso | first2 = ÂNgela | last3 = Barroso | first3 = M. FáTima | last4 = Soares | first4 = DéBora | last5 = Oliveira | first5 = M.B.P.P. | last6 = Delerue-Matos | first6 = Cristina | journal = Food Chemistry | volume = 120 | pages = 960 | issue = 4}}</ref><ref name="  Leszczyńska">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/j.jfca.2008.10.025 | title = Effects of some processing methods on nitrate and nitrite changes in cruciferous vegetables | year = 2009 | last1 = Leszczyńska | first1 = Teresa | last2 = Filipiak-Florkiewicz | first2 = Agnieszka | last3 = Cieślik | first3 = Ewa | last4 = Sikora | first4 = ElżBieta | last5 = Pisulewski | first5 = Paweł M. | journal = Journal of Food Composition and Analysis | volume = 22 | pages = 315 | issue = 4 }}</ref>[[烹饪|烹饪]]蔬菜的过程中可能造成[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]的流失，亚硝酸盐的损失却不显著。<ref name="  Leszczyńska"/>未经加工的肉类含有0.4-0.5 mg/kg亚硝酸盐和4–7 mg/kg硝酸盐，而腌渍过的肉中含有10–30 mg/kg硝酸盐。<ref name="sciencedirect.com"/>亚硝酸盐在动物组织中的代谢产物通常是一种重要的[[神经递质|神经递质]][[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]]。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/0378-4347 (94)00310-6 | title = Measurement of nitrite and nitrate levels in biological samples by capillary electrophoresis | year = 1994 | last1 = Meulemans | first1 = A. | last2 = Delsenne | first2 = F. | journal = Journal of Chromatography B: Biomedical Sciences and Applications | volume = 660 | pages = 401 | issue = 2}}</ref>一氧化氮最初可以由[[精氨酸|精氨酸]]通过[[一氧化氮合成酶|一氧化氮合成酶]]产生或者来源于消化吸收的[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]和[[亚硝酸盐|亚硝酸盐]]。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1006/niox.1998.0187 | pmid = 9851368 | title = Nitrogen Oxides and Hydroxyguanidines: Formation of Donors of Nitric and Nitrous Oxides and Possible Relevance to Nitrous Oxide Formation by Nitric Oxide Synthase | first2 = A | year = 1998 | last2 = Srinivasan | last1 = Southan | first1 = G | journal = Nitric Oxide | volume = 2 | issue = 4 | pages = 270}}</ref>早期关于亚硝酸盐对人体负面影响的研究提前使人们认识到一氧化氮在人体代谢中的重要地位，并且知道了人体本身会内源性地产生一氧化氮。

=== 食品添加剂 ===
亚硝酸钠作为食品添加剂，不仅可以对鱼类、肉类食品进行染色和保鲜，原理是：亚硝酸盐在酸性条件下分解产生亚硝基（ NO ），亚硝基会很快与[[肌红蛋白|肌红蛋白]]反应生成稳定、鲜艳、亮红色的亚硝化肌红蛋白。使肉制品保持稳定的鲜艳红色。因此特别适用于[[午餐肉|午餐肉]]、[[火腿肠|火腿香肠]]等，而[[红烧肉|红烧肉]]罐头、清炖猪肉罐头、炖肘子等肉制品使用自然色泽，一般不添加亚硝酸钠作为[[护色剂|护色剂]]。亚硝酸钠的[[食品添加剂国际编码系统|INS号]]是250，因而有些食品标签上写明了使用250号添加剂，即为亚硝酸钠的讳称。 

亚硝酸钠还可以抑制[[肉毒杆菌|肉毒杆菌]]的生长。后者可以产生[[肉毒杆菌毒素|肉毒杆菌毒素]]，造成食物中毒。在欧盟标准下，亚硝酸钠只能以不高于0.6%的含量与食用盐混合使用，它的[[E编码|E编码]]是E250。对[[亚硝酸钾|亚硝酸钾]]的标准与之类似。

这种化合物可以抑制细菌生长，相应的，在含量比较高的状况下它也对包括人的动物表现明显的毒性。亚硝酸钠对鼠的[[半数致死量|半数致死量]]为180 mg/kg，对人的已知[[最低致死量|最低致死量]]为71 mg/kg，就是说一个重65 kg的人可能被最低4.615[[克|g]]该种物质致死。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://msds.chem.ox.ac.uk/SO/sodium_nitrite.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2011-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111211073524/http://msds.chem.ox.ac.uk/SO/sodium_nitrite.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>为了避免被误食，混有亚硝酸钠的氯化钠（被用于非饮食用途）往往被染成浅红色。

=== 药用 ===
近期的研究中发现亚硝酸钠对于扩张血管、改善血液循环有显著效果，包括对[[镰刀型红血球疾病|镰刀型红血球疾病]]、[[氰化物|氰化物]]中毒、[[心肌梗死|心肌梗死]]、[[脑动脉瘤|脑动脉瘤]]和[[肺动脉高压|肺动脉高压]]去打等的应用前景，其中一些疾病目前可以导致婴儿死亡。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2005-09-05-hot-dog-drug_x.htm | author = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | title = Hot dog preservative could be disease cure | date = 9/5/2005 | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archive-date = 2011-08-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110807135015/http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2005-09-05-hot-dog-drug_x.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn8643 | title = Food preservative fights cystic fibrosis complication | date = 27 January 2006 | publisher = NewScientist.com | author = Roxanne Khamsi | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archive-date = 2008-09-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080917151255/http://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn8643 | dead-url = no }}</ref>静脉注射亚硝酸钠现在已经被用于氰化物中毒的急救。（参见[[氰化物#解毒|氰化物#解毒]]）

=== 化工用途 ===
亚硝酸钠被用于[[胺|胺]]向[[重氮化合物|重氮化合物]]的转化，而N<sub>2</sub>集团具有很好的离去性，生产应用中通过这样的反应来取代氨基。

实验室中，亚硝酸钠也被用于处理过量的[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ehs.neu.edu/hazardous_waste/fact_sheets/sodium_azide/ | work = Hazardous Waste Management | title = Sodium Azide | publisher = [[Northeastern_University|Northeastern University]] | date = March 2003 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071104105622/http://www.ehs.neu.edu/hazardous_waste/fact_sheets/sodium_azide/ | archivedate = 2007-11-04 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title = Prudent practices in the laboratory: handling and disposal of chemicals | year = 1995 | publisher = [[National_Academy_Press|National Academy Press]] | location = Washington, D.C. | isbn = 0309052297 | url = http://books.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=4911&page=165 | author = Committee on Prudent Practices for Handling, Storage, and Disposal of Chemicals in Laboratories, Board on Chemical Sciences and Technology, Commission on Physical Sciences, Mathematics, and Applications, National Research Council. | access-date = 2011-06-27 | archive-date = 2015-03-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150325031033/http://books.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=4911 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>
这是因为在酸性条件下，亚硝酸钠与叠氮化钠发生如下反应：

<math>\rm 2NaN_3 + 2NaNO_2 + 2H^+ {=\!=\!=} 3N_2 \uparrow + 2NO + 2Na^+ + 2H_2O </math>

亚硝酸钠被加热到较高的温度（在330 °C以上）后，可以分解产生[[氧化钠|氧化钠]]、红棕色的[[二氧化氮|二氧化氮]]和[[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]]。<ref>需要注意的是，该反应[[可逆|可逆]]，故生成的气体会与氧化钠重新化合成亚硝酸钠，因而实验现象并不明显，也不适合实际应用</ref>

<math>\rm 2NaNO_2 \stackrel{\Delta}{=\!=\!=} Na_2O + NO \uparrow + NO_2 \uparrow </math>

氧化钠可以吸收二氧化碳产生[[碳酸钠|碳酸钠]]，这有可能避免了第一个[[潜水艇|潜水艇]]中的船员窒息于高浓度的[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]。<ref>[http://www.journalarchive.jst.go.jp/english/jnlabstract_en.php?cdjournal=bcsj1926&cdvol=54&noissue=5&startpage=1385. Hoshino Y., Utsunomiya T., Abe O. The Thermal Decomposition of Sodium Nitrate and the Effects of Several Oxides on the Decomposition. // Bulletin of the Chemical Society of Japan Vol. 54, No.5（1981）. - p.1389.]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

== 健康关注 ==
过量的亚硝酸钠会致癌。亚硝酸钠在烹调和消化过程中会和食物中的胺反应，产生[[致癌物质|致癌物质]][[亚硝胺|亚硝胺]]类化合物。传统食品中也存在亚硝胺，例如[[腌肉|腌肉]]和[[咸鱼干|咸鱼干]]。在19世纪20年代，美国一次重要的肉制品腌渍工艺的改进减少了69%的亚硝酸盐使用，这使得当时胃癌患者的死亡率骤减。<ref>[http://ije.oxfordjournals.org/content/30/1/181.full "The epidemiological enigma of gastric cancer rates in the US: was grandmother's sausage the cause?"] {{Wayback|url=http://ije.oxfordjournals.org/content/30/1/181.full |date=20110511082047 }}, International Journal of Epidemiology (2000) accessdate 2000-08-01</ref>而在1970年前后，人们发现[[抗坏血酸|抗坏血酸]]（即[[维生素C|维生素C]]）可以有效抑制亚硝胺的产生。<ref>{{cite journal | url = http://carcin.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/10/2/397 | title = The inhibition of bacterially mediated N-nitrosation by vitamin C: relevance to the inhibition of endogenous N-nitrosation in the achlorhydric stomach | journal = Carcinogenesis | year = 1989 | volume = 10 | issue = 2 | pages = 397–399 | author = C.W. Mackerness, S.A. Leach, M.H. Thompson and M.J. Hill | doi = 10.1093/carcin/10.2.397 | pmid = 2492212 | access-date = 2011-06-27 | archive-date = 2007-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070127014309/http://carcin.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/10/2/397 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>这使得美国要求肉制品中必须含有至少550ppm的抗坏血酸。制造商有时会使用成本更低但效果相当的[[异抗坏血酸|异抗坏血酸]]作为替代。制造商也会添加[[α-生育酚|α-生育酚]]（即[[维生素E|维生素E]]）来起到进一步效果。上述三种化合物均通过它们的[[抗氧化性|抗氧化性]]来抑制亚硝胺的产生。异抗坏血酸为例，它可以通过[[氧化还原|氧化还原]]作用将亚硝酸钠的转化物[[亚硝酸酐|亚硝酸酐]]还原为[[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]]，而自身被氧化为[[脱氢抗坏血酸|脱氢抗坏血酸]]。<ref>http://lpi.oregonstate.edu/f-w00/nitrosamine.html {{Wayback|url=http://lpi.oregonstate.edu/f-w00/nitrosamine.html |date=20150302051145 }} Nitrosamines and Cancer by Richard A. Scanlan, Ph.D.</ref>

一项最近的研究揭示了长期使用腌渍肉制品与[[慢性阻塞性肺病|COPD]]之间的关系。研究者认为这类肉制品中高含量的亚硝酸盐是导致这类[[肺病|肺病]]的重要因素，但是目前还没有得到理论性的证实。同时这项研究并没有证明亚硝酸盐会提高这类肺病的发病率，而仅仅只是存在某种联系。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.webmd.com/news/20070417/study-copd-cured-meats-may-be-linked | title = Study: Cured Meats, COPD May Be Linked | author = Miranda Hitti | publisher = WebMD Medical News | date = 17 April 2007 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archive-date = 2009-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090405132256/http://www.webmd.com/news/20070417/study-copd-cured-meats-may-be-linked | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1164/rccm.200607-969OC | pmc = 1899290 | title = Cured Meat Consumption, Lung Function, and Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease among United States Adults | pmid = 17255565 | year = 2007 | last1 = Jiang | first1 = R. | last2 = Paik | first2 = D. C. | last3 = Hankinson | first3 = J. L. | last4 = Barr | first4 = R. G. | journal = American Journal of Respiratory and Critical Care Medicine | volume = 175 | issue = 8 | pages = 798}}</ref>

=== 反应机理 ===
致癌物质亚硝胺产生于食物中天然含有的[[胺|胺]]类与加工肉制品中[[亚硝酸盐|亚硝酸盐]]的[[化学反应|化学反应]]。

:R<sub>2</sub>NH（胺） + NaNO<sub>2</sub>（亚硝酸钠）→ R<sub>2</sub>N-N=O（亚硝胺）

在酸性环境（例如胃液）中火加热条件（例如烹饪过程）下，亚硝胺可以形成[[重氮盐|重氮盐]]。

:R<sub>2</sub>N-N=O（亚硝胺） +（酸性环境或加热条件）→ R-N<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>（重氮盐）

特定的亚硝胺类化合物，例如[[N-亚硝胺|N-亚硝胺]]<ref name=najm2001>{{cite journal|title=NDMA Formation in Water and Wastewater|author= Najm, Issam; Trussell, R. Rhodes|journal=Journal AWWA|volume=93|issue=2|date=February 2001|pages=92–99}}</ref>和[[N-亚硝基四氢吡咯|N-亚硝基四氢吡咯]]<ref name=bills1973>{{cite journal|title=Potential precursors of N-nitrosopyrrolidine in bacon and other fried foods|author=Donald D. Bills, Kjell I. Hildrum, Richard A. Scanlan, Leonard M. Libbey|journal=J. Agric. Food Chem.|volume=21|issue=5|date=May 1973|pages=876–877|doi=10.1021/jf60189a029|pmid=4739004}}</ref>可以产生[[碳正离子|碳正离子]]与细胞中的生物[[亲核试剂|亲核试剂]]发生反应（例如[[DNA|DNA]]或[[酶|酶]]）。

:R-N<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>（重氮盐）→ R<sup>+</sup>（碳正离子） + N<sub>2</sub>（离去基团） + :Nu（生物亲核试剂）→ R-Nu

一旦这样的[[SN1反应|亲核取代]]发生在一个生物大分子上的关键部位，就可能破坏细胞的正常功能，导致细胞[[癌变|癌变]]或[[细胞凋亡|细胞凋亡]]。

